ygData.messageBody:
It does Not always give you a boost, I have noticed. If you are allready
considered above indifferent, it will not change anything.
and, you dont have to be right next to the person to use it. it works across
the counter
---

I am camped in FP right now, and I'll make a real effort to test this
out this weekend. I had a nice load of bronze weapons to sell so I went
around trying to see who would give me the most money already though.
Maybe it was one of those always doing the same thing wrong things,
where the next time I sit down to try it will be so simple I kick
myself...
--
We now return to the non-stop rock.

Matt DeBarger
